text: Konstantin Vaterkampf (, born 1888, date of death unknown) was a Russian Olympic fencer. He competed in the individual sabre event at the 1912 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1888 births Category:Year of death missing Category:Russian male fencers Category:Olympic fencers of Russia Category:Fencers at the 1912 Summer Olympics
